_sText:
This map is like a futuristic community. It is a small section of a huge city that uses an irrigation system to supply each section with water. This section just happens to be on the delta of the river, thus the name.

Please note that I was not trying to capture a realistic look of a building. As I said before it was kind of "futuristic"

UPDATE 7/10
I added some more props all around, such as bushes of different types, to more models in the market. I also added street lamps arpund the place to add to the maps atmosphere

UPDATE 7/21
So the map is finally done. I optimized a bunch, fixed framerate problems, and 3d skyboxed.
